metadata.name: OMG!!LOL
metadata.description:
On a beautiful sunny day, the two of us came together for ice cream.
She ordered a double, and I was taking pictures of her looking so happy, and I ended up with this amazing shot! LOL!
It's just like her to laugh it off without crying or getting angry!

よく晴れた日、2人でアイスを食べにきた。
ダブルを頼んで嬉しそうな彼女を撮っていたらすごい写真が撮れっちゃった！笑
泣いたり怒ったりせず笑い飛ばすところが彼女らしい
